OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHealth staff win Covid     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbonus after legal threat   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has agreed to fund a    
OL,6, one-off bonus for health workers who   
OL,7, missed out previously because they     
OL,8, worked for non-NHS organisations.      
OL,10,FA payment of at least #1,655 was agreed
OL,11,Fas part of the NHS pay deal in England 
OL,12,Fthis year, to recognise the pressure of
OL,13,Fthe Covid pandemic on staff.           
OL,15,FBut the BBC recently reported thousands
OL,16,Fof outsourced staff did not qualify and
OL,17,Femployers had launched legal action.   
OL,19,FTheir employers can now apply for      
OL,20,Ffunding to cover the payments.         
